    <item>
      <title>Install matplotlib on mac sierra</title>
      <link>https://yantonov.com/post/2017-01-05-install-matplotlib-on-mac-sierra/</link>
      <guid>https://yantonov.com/post/2017-01-05-install-matplotlib-on-mac-sierra/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Jan 2017 22:38:37 +0500</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;During matplotlib installation (for python3) some error may occured:&lt;br&gt;
&amp;lsquo;The following required packages can not be built:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;freetype&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;png&amp;rsquo;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thats why some additional steps may be required:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;install &lt;a href=&#34;http://brew.sh&#34;&gt;homebrew&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;install pkg-config&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew install pkg-config
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;install freetype&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew install freetype
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start=&#34;4&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;install matplotlib&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip3 install matplotlib
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
